apps.localizedDescription:
Built-into Instagram
• Runs inside Instagram, so no need to install a separate app or service. It also uses Instagram private API for Analytics and other features.

Profile Analyzer
• Scans your Instagram profile to provide in-depth analysis, including who unfollowed you, who doesn't follow you back, and any changes to their profiles (picture, username, full name, privacy, and verification).

Media Downloader
• Downloads any Instagram media, including posts, stories, reels, post audio, and direct messages.

Privacy
• View stories and read direct messages without sending seen receipts, Send them manually with a single tap.

Messages
• Keep unsent messages, stop sending typing and screenshot notifications, download audio messages, save vanish media messages, confirm call buttons, and more.

Utilities & Customization
• Confirm clicking like and follow buttons, copy captions, comments and bios, format stories, posts and last active dates to a more detailed date format.

Cracked by @Blatant and @Choco

apps.localizedDescription:
This tweak makes Spotify think you have a Premium subscription, granting free listening and provides some additional features like custom lyrics.

These features are server sided and won't work:
• Very High audio quality
• Native playlist downloading
• Jam
• AI DJ/Playlist

To open Spotify links, use OpenSpotifySafariExtension. Remember to activate it and allow access in Settings > Safari > Extensions.

Source: https://github.com/whoeevee/EeveeSpotify

apps.subtitle: A tweak to get Spotify Premium for free
